<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA81">
<l>kālaṉaiyum veṉṟōṅ kaṭunarakaṅ kaikaḻaṉṟō</l>
<l>mēlai yiruviṉaiyum vēraṟuttōṅ - kōla</l>
<l>varaṇā ravintaḻiya ventīyam peytāṉ</l>
<l>caraṇāra vintaṅkaḷ cārntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have vanquished Death, we have loosened with [our] hands severe hell</l>
<l>and we have henceforth cut of the root of the two [kinds] of karma – approaching</l>
<l>the beautiful feet lotuses of him who shot an arrow with hot fire</l>
<l>so that those of the [three] strongholds ceased [and] perished.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
